==English==
===Intransitive verb===
'''[[mince]] [[words]]'''
#{{idiom}} to [[restrain]] oneself in a [[conversation]] and say less than one wants to, out of fear of offending the listener.  (Usually used in the negative.)
#: ''Let's not '''mince words'''.  Your idea is ridiculous.''

